{"tid":106960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到仆街] 港人之恥 趙公允 趙公亮 欺騙全球消費者 呃公帑資助","createTime":"2017-02-04T05:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T06:32:19.000Z","uid":13504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7fe8fd4349f264b92dc8ef85af9cef78c08f2d","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"簡單講講個故事<br />\n大約係呢兩條仆街,起集資網站推出集資以下兩款PRODUCT<br />\nArist 智能咖啡機 以及<br />\nZNAPS 磁能充電線<br />\n<br />\n兩次都集完資無貨出,仲要有獎拎,用埋香港人公帑的資助!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n節錄自APPLE NEWS <br />\n&quot;兩款走數產品不單在眾籌網站吸金近2,500萬港元，更獲政府嘉許，以公帑資助。事件涉及全球7萬多個各國投資者，有人曾向香港及美國警方報案，卻不獲受理。&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160630/19675940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160630%2F19675940&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f5f74661\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160630%2F19675940&h=baa6e394\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160630/19675940</a><br />\n<br />\nZnaps磁能充電線走數時序<br />\n2015年：<br />\n7月：Znaps磁能線在加拿大Kickstarter集資約1,800萬港元，原定2015年11月發貨<br />\n10月：2016年香港資訊及通訊科技獎開始接受報名<br />\n11-12月：Znaps稱未能通過品質測試，需延期發貨<br />\n12月：趙公允妻子劉志芳註冊香港公司Znaps Limited，申請參加獎項<br />\n<br />\n2016年：<br />\n4月：Znaps Limited獲初創企業銅獎<br />\n6月：Znaps仍未公佈發貨時間，被投資者批評是騙局；趙公允拒回應傳媒查詢<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n補充上面時序,後來到上年年尾,ZNAPS 寄EMAIL俾集資者話佢地ORDER資料唔見曬,話會作出REFUND,到今日依家無人收到一毫子的退款<br />\nKICKSTARTER PAGE上面仲有全球勁多集資者投訴未收到產品,又未收到REFUND<br />\n政府審查求其,亂用公帑,間接幫呢D仆街呃人,仲要做臭曬香港個名!"},{"pid":"a769dc27da5a57fa70ba320a0c9f4a3d68f95ba9","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/nelson-8mar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fnelson-8mar.jpg&h=a950a832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩條仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160630/small/30la2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160630%2Fsmall%2F30la2p1.jpg&h=6e585d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條仆街用完咖啡機呃人<br />\n推埋個老婆GLORIA LAU出來,用佢個名開ZNAPS繼續呃人"},{"pid":"cc607d120be81e56caa63de29bd766509de329dc","tid":106960,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"集資網 根本一堆騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d246fe20d8af5673cb57d3f5aeea7b7a295337","tid":106960,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"磁能線"},{"pid":"228c662c028d06b23252d174aef0f9a8323e0911","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"推, 大家真係唔好去集資網買任何野<br />\nKICKSTARTER 係完全不負責任"},{"pid":"fabd04ad5ad69748c6a7563c6dd4eb0862573e29","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"954eb725247117ff855e9f210f3b52473dfaffff","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaaeaefdce874ee75a8b5d4dd4cbe928a2d665bb","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7b5c6a3bcb7e56c26b533f0443ef8fe4d4a31cf","tid":106960,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fb45419e790a413b960302caa7a611584ac6403","tid":106960,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0091271b01f909e522985a3a2302a77c9c978f39","tid":106960,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mpjQsk&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f80069b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk</a><br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b8b8e016f285b615eabfd47b3faa45fe16248d","tid":106960,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mpjQsk&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f80069b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk</a><br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去年《蘋果》踢爆，「磁能線」Znaps於眾籌網站Kickstarter推出「磁能線」集資1800萬元後擬似走數，遲遲未發貨，其後更以香港公司Znaps Limited（施納士）名義，獲港府頒發「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」初創企業銅獎。政府今日宣佈，資訊科技總監辦公室在諮詢「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」督導委員會後，決定取消Znaps Limited的得獎資格。<br />\n<br />\n去年《蘋果》揭發，以走數「聞名」的眾籌項目智能咖啡機，其主事人趙公允的妻子劉志芳，原來正是Znaps的幕後話事人，去年底更以香港公司Znaps Limited名義，奪得政府主辦的香港資訊及通訊科技獎獎項，觸發違規參賽疑團，惟當局調查近月後，最終決定「放生」該公司，拒撤回獎項。<br />\n事隔半年，資科辦表示，在檢視所有資料及聽取督委會的意見後，認為Znaps Limited未能完全符合參賽資格，尤其有關「產品須已推出巿場最少三個月」的規定。故此，資科辦決定取消其得奬資格。<br />\n政府又指，「2017香港資訊及通訊科技獎」，資科辦已落實改善措施，加強檢視參賽項目、籌辦機構核實參賽資格的程序和評審工作。資科辦會繼續與各界合作，透過這個廣受認同的專業獎項，促進本地資訊及通訊科技業的發展。"},{"pid":"3671b85a253027b77bf172bf159192c727b3021a","tid":106960,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mpjQsk&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f80069b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mpjQsk</a><br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去年《蘋果》踢爆，「磁能線」Znaps於眾籌網站Kickstarter推出「磁能線」集資1800萬元後擬似走數，遲遲未發貨，其後更以香港公司Znaps Limited（施納士）名義，獲港府頒發「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」初創企業銅獎。政府今日宣佈，資訊科技總監辦公室在諮詢「香港資訊及通訊科技獎」督導委員會後，決定取消Znaps Limited的得獎資格。<br />\n<br />\n去年《蘋果》揭發，以走數「聞名」的眾籌項目智能咖啡機，其主事人趙公允的妻子劉志芳，原來正是Znaps的幕後話事人，去年底更以香港公司Znaps Limited名義，奪得政府主辦的香港資訊及通訊科技獎獎項，觸發違規參賽疑團，惟當局調查近月後，最終決定「放生」該公司，拒撤回獎項。<br />\n事隔半年，資科辦表示，在檢視所有資料及聽取督委會的意見後，認為Znaps Limited未能完全符合參賽資格，尤其有關「產品須已推出巿場最少三個月」的規定。故此，資科辦決定取消其得奬資格。<br />\n政府又指，「2017香港資訊及通訊科技獎」，資科辦已落實改善措施，加強檢視參賽項目、籌辦機構核實參賽資格的程序和評審工作。資科辦會繼續與各界合作，透過這個廣受認同的專業獎項，促進本地資訊及通訊科技業的發展。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff361d4177554c7e8c4b956b089477f887a3bc3","tid":106960,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"趙公允facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/faifaichiu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffaifaichiu&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=583882ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/faifaichiu</a><br />\n<br />\n趙公允大面西老婆Gloria Lau facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gloria.lau.5648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgloria.lau.5648&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ae452c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gloria.lau.5648</a>"},{"pid":"054addd0a428be647937ca47ea344cea86858522","tid":106960,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/faifaichiu/posts/10155014641629636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffaifaichiu%2Fposts%2F10155014641629636&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9b8b7deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/faifaichiu/posts/10155014641629636</a><br />\n<br />\n用你地D錢飛去vegas繼續呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xdMFZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xdMFZM.png&h=6b087481&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9294870c9d82a077274feed26f04779324d33173","tid":106960,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b523a2e666c159c4b018b233dd8faf553ed8766","tid":106960,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"出貨未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}